cc:Work.dc:title: Xenia Sunrise
cc:Work.dc:description: Xenia is standing in front of the viewer, looking directly. She's having golden-red hair, a t-shirt with Linux logo, purple jacket and glasses. In the background there's a sunrise shinning on her and a huge view at the mountains and clouds. She's surrounded by golden leaves, symbolizing the current weather in UTC+1 Canary Islands.
